quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,6,"Ngal balla ko fodoore Alla wonunoo. Laatagol mayre ngol …ďeyday gom…óim…ďe …ďen pellital e fodoore Alla nden. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe hino majjiraa …óum sabu keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe ngun."
  30,7,"∆Āe anndaa gom…óinal e √Īaawooje sari'a. Ko …ďe anndii woo ko ko fee√Īi e nguurndam aduna …óam e ko yowondiri e …óa…ď…ďere nguuree ma…ď…ďe e mahugol ngaddamaaku. Kono kam…ďe e fii laakara on won…óo ho…óo nguurndam …óam tigi, ko …ďe …óuurnii …ďe, …ďe tefataa fii mun."
  30,8,"E …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennoo…ďe miijitaaki fii no Alla tagiri wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe O fotindiri …ói? Alla tagiraali kammuli …óin e leydi ndin si wanaa goona, O tagiraali …ói fijindaaru, O wa…óanii …ói kadi lajal happaangal heddagol ka aduna. Anndee non, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, ko yeddu…ďe hawroygol e Joomi ma…ď…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal, ko …óum ha…ói …ďe hebloranagol nden √Īalnde golle mo∆ī∆īe weltinay…óe Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  30,9,"E …ďee yiilaaki ka leydi …ďe taskoo ko honno battane mofte fennunoo…ďe …ďen ado ma…ď…ďe wa'unoo? ∆Āen laatino …ďur…ďe doole, …ďe wuurniti leydi ndin remuruuji, …ďe wuuri e mayri …ďuri ko …ďee wuuri e mayri kon. Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addani …ďe hujjaaji …ďanngin…ói gootaaku Alla ngun, kono …ďe fenni. Alla too√Īiraa …ďe halkugol …ďe ngol, kono non, ko ko'e ma…ď…ďe …ďe wonunoo e too√Īirde jolnorgol jolirde halkaare sabu keefaraagu ma…ď…ďe ngun ."
  30,10,"Refti ko wonunoo battane …ďen bonnirnoo…ďe golle mun sirkangol Alla e golle bon…óe, ko bone …ďur…óo bondne; tawde …ďe fennii Aayeeje Alla …óen, …ďe laatii e jalkitugol …óe."
  30,11,"Ko Alla woni fu…ó…óir…óo tagu ngun no ngu ko aldah e yeru gadii…óo, refti O gayna fii maggu, refti O ruttita ngu; refti ko ka Makko Kanko tun ruttete…óon √Ďalnde Darngal fii hasbeede yo…ďee."
  30,12,"√Ďalnde Darngal ngal dorotoo, bombe …ďen ta∆īoyto e yurmeende Alla, tawde hujja ma…ď…ďe e yeddugol Alla ngol wonii bolle puy…óe."
  30,13,"Woodanoytaa…ďe e kafidii…ói ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe rewynoo …óin aduna, ko tefana …ďe da…óugol lepte …óen, wurin …óin yeddoyay kafidu…ďe…ói …ďen; …ói hoynoya …ďe ka …ďe hatonjinnoo e ma…ď…ďe, kono …ói hattanaa e, tawde …ďe fotay ka halkaare."
  30,14,"√Ďalnde Darngal ngal darii, nden √Īalnde yim…ďe …ďen sertiroyay e njo…ďdi yeru no …ďe gollirnoo aduna non: wo…ó…ďe towniroyee ka Aljannaaji dow, wo…ó…ďe jippiniroyee ley ka Yiite."
  30,15,"Si ko …ďen gom…óim…ďe Alla …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe weltinay…óe Mo, …ďen …óon wonoyay e beeli Aljanna hi…ďe weltiro ko …ďe neeminirtee ton e neemaaji duumotoo…ói poomaa."